  "description": "<p><strong>财富中文网(www.FORTUNEChina.com)今晚与英文网全球同步发布2013年《财富》世界500强排行榜，壳牌石油蝉联榜首。中国上榜公司数量达到95家。科技公司中，三星电子第14，苹果第19。</strong>按目前的势头，2015年中美大公司有可能在榜单上平分秋色。但在数量连年上升同时，中国上榜公司显现出的结构失衡和杠杆率过高两大问题值得警惕。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e5c8786/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243893.htm&amp;t=2013%E3%80%8A%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C%E3%80%8B500%E5%BC%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%82%89%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E7%AC%AC14+%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%AC%AC19\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243893.htm&amp;t=2013%E3%80%8A%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C%E3%80%8B500%E5%BC%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%82%89%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E7%AC%AC14+%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%AC%AC19\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243893.htm&amp;t=2013%E3%80%8A%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C%E3%80%8B500%E5%BC%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%82%89%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E7%AC%AC14+%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%AC%AC19\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243893.htm&amp;t=2013%E3%80%8A%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C%E3%80%8B500%E5%BC%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%82%89%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E7%AC%AC14+%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%AC%AC19\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243893.htm&amp;t=2013%E3%80%8A%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C%E3%80%8B500%E5%BC%B